        "Title": "Bravuomo&apos;s daring escape",
        "Location": "LOCATION_COASTALTOWN_NIGHT",
        "PublicId": "104969947231",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/CoastalTown/_scene_mamba.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 853b4070-99b1-45da-938b-6fa7947eb7cd).Image",
        "Description": "Salvatore Bravuomo, a Lawyer born in Sapienza wants to disappear and seek a different, better life. To do this he has asked us to eliminate 2 people in his name:\r\r-Marco Abiatti, a politician desperate on ensuring his demise.\r\r-Cristina Dionisi, Bravuomo&apos;s passionate lover who will stop at nothing to track him down.\r\rBravuomo has asked us to incapacitate him and place him in a secure location so he can make a swift exit from the country free from identification.",
